Package: DrDesign
Type: Package
Title: Shiny Apps for Agricultural Experimental Data Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Saurav", family = "Singla", email = "saurav@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Allows users to perform analysis of Agricultural experimental data in CRD/RBD, factorial design, pooled ANOVA, split-plot, and correlation-regression analysis. It is further extended to plant breeding trails for Multi Environmental Trait Analysis. It is capable of producing clean and systematic pdf and word based outputs. A Graphical User Interface will pop up on using the functions in this package.
